sequenceDiagram
    participant You
    participant TG as Telegram (cloud)
    participant Bot as Work Bot<br/>(BotFather token)
    participant GW as Work Gateway<br/>~/gateways/work/
    participant Brain as Shared Brain<br/>(memories/, skills/)
    participant LLM as Xiaomi MiMo
    participant OR as OpenRouter<br/>(fallback)

    You->>TG: "what did I commit yesterday?"
    TG->>Bot: forwards via bot token
    Bot->>GW: gateway picks up message
    GW->>Brain: read MEMORY.md + relevant skills
    GW->>LLM: prompt + context + tools
    alt MiMo healthy
        LLM-->>GW: response
    else MiMo down / 401
        GW->>OR: same request, fallback model
        OR-->>GW: response
    end
    GW->>Brain: save anything important to MEMORY.md
    GW->>Bot: formatted reply
    Bot->>TG: send reply
    TG->>You: message arrives
